Title: The Implant
Plot: Jerry dumps his girlfriend after Elaine says her figure is the result of implants. Kramer claims to have seen Salman Rushdie at the health club. By accident Elaine later discovers the breasts are real. George accompanies his current girlfriend to Detroit for her aunt's wake. While there he tries to get a copy of her death certificate so he can get a 50% discount on the airfare.
GuestStars: Teri Hatcher, Megan Mullally, Carol Rosenthal, Donald Bishop, Tony Amendola, Kieran Mulroney, Peggy Stewart, Bruce E. Morrow, Susan Beaubian
